{"name":"甘宁","nameCn":"","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/a6/b9/19371_crt_5Qhmn.jpg","info":"<li><span>性别: </span>男</li>","detail":"甘宁是日本KOEI（现KOEI TECMO）公司开发的《真·三国无双》系列游戏中的人物。<br />性情豪迈的热血汉子。曾经在江上当过水贼，时人听见甘宁腰间悬挂的铜铃响声就会远远遁逃，因此拥有“铃之甘宁”的异名。在夏口之战中杀死孙权部将·凌操，因而后来在归降孙权后被凌操之子·凌统敌视；然而在日后的种种征战中，甘宁与凌统多次并肩作战，由不共戴天之仇变成了偶尔闹闹别扭的同伴。<br />甘宁在游戏1-4代的武器是甲刀，5代的武器是双钩“钩月”，6代的得意武器是锁镰。","jobs":[{"href":"/subject/68106","name":"真・三國無双3 Empires","nameCn":"真三国无双3 帝国","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/7c/e3/68106_665mE.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/23082","name":"真・三國無双 VS","nameCn":"真·三国无双 VS","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/87/46/23082_bTtAx.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"三浦祥朗","castHref":"/person/4304","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/1a/96/4304_prsn_gmSRv.jpg"},{"href":"/subject/68109","name":"真・三國無双4 Empires","nameCn":"真・三國無双4 Empires","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/94/85/68109_U6J6a.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/68108","name":"真・三國無双4 猛将伝","nameCn":"真·三国无双4 猛将传","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/93/4c/68108_4645v.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/30193","name":"真·三国无双 NEXT","nameCn":"真·三国无双 NEXT","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/de/81/30193_Cw144.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"三浦祥朗","castHref":"/person/4304","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/1a/96/4304_prsn_gmSRv.jpg"},{"href":"/subject/8376","name":"真・三國無双 2nd Evolution","nameCn":"真·三国无双 二度进化","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/c1/1c/8376_3T9Kz.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"三浦祥朗","castHref":"/person/4304","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/1a/96/4304_prsn_gmSRv.jpg"},{"href":"/subject/68110","name":"真・三國無双6 Empires","nameCn":"真·三国无双6 帝国","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/af/ad/68110_k0dLE.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/56713","name":"真・三國無双7","nameCn":"真·三国无